---
const email = 'contact@agentskillforge.com';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>agentskillforge.com - Practical agentic workflow agents</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="agentskillforge.com helps small businesses turn agentic AI into practical, long-running workflow agents teams can shape to business goals (with training)."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-brand-secondary/10 bg-brand-background/80 backdrop-blur">
			<div class="container flex h-16 items-center justify-between">
				<a href="#top" class="flex items-center gap-3 font-semibold tracking-tight">
					<img
						src="/agentskillforge-logo-asf-alt2.png"
						alt="agentskillforge logo"
						class="h-7 w-auto"
					/>
					<span class="text-brand-secondary">agentskillforge.com</span>
				</a>
				<nav class="hidden items-center gap-6 text-sm md:flex">
					<a class="text-brand-secondary/70 hover:text-brand-secondary" href="#services">Services</a>
					<a class="text-brand-secondary/70 hover:text-brand-secondary" href="#different">What’s different</a>
					<a class="text-brand-secondary/70 hover:text-brand-secondary" href="#faq">FAQ</a>
					<a
						class="rounded-lg bg-brand-secondary px-4 py-2 text-white hover:bg-brand-secondary/90"
						href="#contact">Contact</a>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>

		<main id="top">
			<section class="container py-14 md:py-20">
				<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
					<div>
						<img
							src="/ai_adoption_levels.png"
							alt="AI adoption levels"
							class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white p-2"
						/>
					</div>

					<div class="max-w-3xl">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
							Is AI working for you yet?
						</h2>

						<div class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-brand-secondary/80">
							<p>Are you using AI one query at a time?</p>
							<p>Is AI just giving helpful advice, or is it actually running your workflows for you?</p>
						</div>

						<p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary/80">
							Building and training multi-agent AI teams transforms how work gets done. At Agent Skill Forge, we put the power of practical agentic AI into your hands. We’re not building a solution and dumping it in your lap, we work alongside your team to enable, train, and govern AI so you can leverage it confidently.
						</p>

						<div class="mt-8">
							<a
								href="#contact"
								class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-brand-primary/90"
							>
								Get your Level 1/2 → Level 4 roadmap
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="container py-14">
				<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-start">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-3xl">One system, Your System</h2>
						<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-brand-secondary/80">
							Your agents should run inside your environment, under your rules. That’s how responsibility stays clear and control stays real.
						</p>

						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-brand-secondary/80">
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Agents hosted on your servers.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Connected to your systems</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Specialist training remains yours</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Governance and auditability stay in-house</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Portability and exit rights on your terms</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="flex justify-start md:justify-end">
						<img
							src="/one-system_circular.png"
							alt="One system, your system"
							class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white p-2"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="container py-14">
				<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-start">
					<div class="flex justify-start md:justify-start">
						<img
							src="/build_trust.png"
							alt="Build trust"
							class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white p-2"
						/>
					</div>

					<div class="max-w-3xl">
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-3xl">Choose a trusted AI Partner</h2>
						<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-brand-secondary/80">
							Today it’s especially difficult to choose an AI partner you can trust. Everyone is making impressive demos but many have no experience building working systems. Delivered software is brittle, and unreliable. You need a partner who knows how to deliver quality and won’t disappear when things go wrong.
						</p>

						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-brand-secondary/80">
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Years of Experience System Designers</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Can show working demos with useful examples</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Reliable systems your business can rely on</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Puts AI tools into your hands</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Partnership and training - we work alongside you</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span>Helps you build continually improving systems</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="container py-16 md:py-20">
				<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
					<div>
						<h1 class="text-balance text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">
							Agentic AI for <span class="text-brand-secondary">real workflows</span>
						</h1>
						<p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary/80">
							We help small businesses turn agentic AI into practical, long-running workflow agents that teams can shape to business goals (with training), not one-off bespoke automation.
						</p>

						<div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
							<a
								href="#services"
								class="rounded-lg border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-brand-secondary hover:bg-brand-background"
							>
								Explore services
							</a>
							<a
								href="#contact"
								class="rounded-lg bg-brand-primary px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-brand-primary/90"
							>
								Get in touch
							</a>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-brand-secondary/70">
							<span class="rounded-full border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-3 py-1">Training included</span>
							<span class="rounded-full border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-3 py-1">Staff enablement</span>
							<span class="rounded-full border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-3 py-1">Long-running agents</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-background to-white p-6">
						<h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Quick overview</h2>
						<ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-brand-secondary/80">
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span><strong>Trainable + shapeable</strong> agents guided toward your business objectives and operating style.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span><strong>Long-running learning agents</strong> built for ongoing work, not one-off automations.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary"></span>
								<span><strong>Staff enablement</strong> so your team can use and govern agents safely.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>

						<div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white p-4">
							<p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-secondary">Best for</p>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-brand-secondary/80">
								Small businesses and their staff who want a practical agentic AI pilot without needing an in-house AI engineering team.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="different" class="border-t border-brand-secondary/10 bg-brand-background">
				<div class="container py-14">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What makes us different</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-brand-secondary/80">
						More than a script or a one-time integration. We build long-running workflow agents your team can shape, learn, and operate.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
						{[
							{ title: 'Long-running learning agents', body: 'Designed for ongoing work and continuous improvement.' },
							{ title: 'Trainable + shapeable', body: 'Guided toward business objectives and your operating style.' },
							{ title: 'Staff enablement', body: 'Education, governance, and rollout support for teams.' },
						].map((c) => (
							<div class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white p-6">
								<h3 class="text-base font-semibold">{c.title}</h3>
								<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary/80">{c.body}</p>
							</div>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="services" class="container py-14">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What we offer (starting menu)</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-brand-secondary/80">Pick a starting point and evolve from there.</p>

				<div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
					{[
						{
							title: 'Consulting',
							body: 'Educate leaders and teams on what agents are, what to automate first, and how to design for outcomes.',
						},
						{
							title: 'Ready-made agentic systems',
							body: 'Packaged, configurable agents for common business workflows.',
						},
						{
							title: 'Pre-trained agents',
							body: 'Starting points tailored to a business’s domain and constraints.',
						},
						{
							title: 'Staff agents / training',
							body: 'Making agentic tools available to staff safely and effectively.',
						},
					].map((s) => (
						<div class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white p-6">
							<h3 class="text-base font-semibold">{s.title}</h3>
							<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary/80">{s.body}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="faq" class="border-t border-brand-secondary/10 bg-brand-background">
				<div class="container py-14">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
					<div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
						<details class="group rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-6 py-4">
							<summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium">What do you mean by “long-running workflow agents”?</summary>
							<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary/80">
								Agents that stay useful over time, supporting ongoing work (and learning) instead of just running once like a script.
							</p>
						</details>
						<details class="group rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-6 py-4">
							<summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium">How is this different from one-off automation?</summary>
							<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary/80">
								We design for outcomes and operating style, then help teams learn, govern, and evolve the system.
							</p>
						</details>
						<details class="group rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-6 py-4">
							<summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium">What should we automate first?</summary>
							<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary/80">
								We start with workflows that benefit from repetition, structure, and clear business goals. Then we scope, train, and ship a pilot.
							</p>
						</details>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="contact" class="container py-14">
				<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Let’s build your first agentic workflow pilot</h2>
						<p class="mt-3 text-brand-secondary/80">Email us and we’ll suggest a smart starting point based on your goals and constraints.</p>
						<div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
							<a
								href={`mailto:${email}?subject=${encodeURIComponent('Agentskillforge - Website Inquiry')}`}
								class="rounded-lg bg-brand-primary px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-brand-primary/90"
							>
								Email {email}
							</a>
							<a
								href="#services"
								class="rounded-lg border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-brand-secondary hover:bg-brand-background"
							>
								See services again
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-white p-6">
						<p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-secondary">What to include in your message</p>
						<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-secondary/80">
							<li>Which workflow(s) you want to improve</li>
							<li>What “success” looks like for your team</li>
							<li>Any constraints (tools, data, compliance)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<footer class="border-t border-brand-secondary/10">
			<div class="container py-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
				<p class="text-sm text-brand-secondary/70">© {year} agentskillforge.com</p>
				<div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
					<a class="text-brand-secondary/70 hover:text-brand-secondary" href="#top">Back to top</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
